    {
      "id": "el_11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 344,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "Independent: P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B)\nDependent:   P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B|A)\n\nIndependent = one event doesn't affect other\nDependent = outcome changes next probability",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1100,
      "version": 1,
