      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Independent: P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B)\nDependent:   P(A ∩ B) = P(A) x P(B|A)\n\nIndependent = one event doesn't affect other\nDependent = outcome changes next probability",
      "autoResize": true,
