    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 278,
      "width": 289,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "P(not A) = 1 - P(A)\nP(at least 1) = 1 - P(none)\n\nConditional: P(A|B) = P(A ∩ B) / P(B)\nBayes: P(A|B) = P(B|A).P(A) / P(B)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
