    {
      "id": "el_17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 278,
      "width": 312,
      "height": 94,
      "text": "1 Coin = 2    n Coins = 2^n\n1 Die  = 6    2 Dice  = 36\n1 Deck = 52 cards (4 suits x 13)\n\nnCr heads in n tosses: P = nCr / 2^n\n2 dice sum=7: 6 ways, sum=2 or 12: 1 way",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
