    },
    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 548,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total = 4+3+5 = 12, Blue = 3\nStep 2: P = favorable/total = 3/12\n\nTRICK:\nP(blue) = blue/total = 3/12 = 1/4\n\n  ┌──── Bag (12 balls) ─────┐\n  │ ●●●●  ○○○  ◎◎◎◎◎       │\n  │ 4Red  3Blue 5Green      │\n  └─────────────────────────┘\n\nAnswer: P(blue) = 1/4 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
