      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total = 4+3+5 = 12, Blue = 3\nStep 2: P = favorable/total = 3/12\n\nTRICK:\nP(blue) = blue/total = 3/12 = 1/4\n\n  ┌──── Bag (12 balls) ─────┐\n  │ ●●●●  ○○○  ◎◎◎◎◎       │\n  │ 4Red  3Blue 5Green      │\n  └─────────────────────────┘\n\nAnswer: P(blue) = 1/4 ✓",
