    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 918,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P(M∪E) = P(M)+P(E)-P(M∩E)\nStep 2: = 0.7+0.8-0.6 = 0.9\n\nTRICK:\nVenn: M only=0.1, Both=0.6, E only=0.2\nP(at least one) = 1-P(neither)\n= 1-0.1 = 0.9\n\n  |M only|Both|E only| Neither\n  | 0.1  |0.6 | 0.2  | = 0.1\n\nAnswer: P(at least one) = 0.9 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
