    {
      "id": "el_79",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1577,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "If the probability of winning a game is 3/8, what are the\nodds in favor of winning and the odds against winning?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 79,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If the probability of winning a game is 3/8, what are the\nodds in favor of winning and the odds against winning?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1620,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 80,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_81",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1642,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P(win)=3/8, P(lose)=5/8\nStep 2: Favor = 3:5, Against = 5:3\n\nTRICK:\nP = p/q → Odds = p:(q-p)\n3/8 → 3:(8-3) = 3:5\nOdds a:b → P = a/(a+b)\n\n  |✓ ✓ ✓ | ✗ ✗ ✗ ✗ ✗|\n  |favor  | against  |\n\nAnswer: Favor 3:5, Against 5:3 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 81,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P(win)=3/8, P(lose)=5/8\nStep 2: Favor = 3:5, Against = 5:3\n\nTRICK:\nP = p/q → Odds = p:(q-p)\n3/8 → 3:(8-3) = 3:5\nOdds a:b → P = a/(a+b)\n\n  |✓ ✓ ✓ | ✗ ✗ ✗ ✗ ✗|\n  |favor  | against  |\n\nAnswer: Favor 3:5, Against 5:3 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
