      "x": 65,
      "y": 1931,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A game costs Rs.10 to play. You roll a die: if you get a 6\nyou win Rs.50, otherwise you win nothing. Is it worth\nplaying based on expected value?",
