    {
      "id": "el_86",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2012,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 159,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: E(X) = 50×(1/6) + 0×(5/6)\n  = 50/6 = Rs.8.33\nStep 2: Net = 8.33-10 = -1.67 (loss)\n\nTRICK:\nE(X) = Sum[value × probability]\nIf E(X) < cost → don't play!\n8.33 < 10 → expected loss\n\nAnswer: Net = -Rs.1.67 (loss) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
