        "type_13"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: E(X) = 50×(1/6) + 0×(5/6)\n  = 50/6 = Rs.8.33\nStep 2: Net = 8.33-10 = -1.67 (loss)\n\nTRICK:\nE(X) = Sum[value × probability]\nIf E(X) < cost → don't play!\n8.33 < 10 → expected loss\n\nAnswer: Net = -Rs.1.67 (loss) ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
