      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1931,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "A square has side 10 cm with a circle of radius 3 cm drawn\nat its center. If a point is chosen at random inside the\nsquare, what is the probability that it lies inside the\ncircle?",
